# Per-box runtime state — NOT tracked.
# node_id differs per box, and the script writes calibration (raw_idle) back to
# this file at runtime, so tracking it makes `git pull` conflict on every node.
# Templates live in configs/ — copy one per box:
#   cp configs/rods_proximity.json python/sensor_config.json
python/sensor_config.json
